Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.98,0:00:13.34,Show Title,,0,0,0,,{\fs142.5\fnGallow Tree\4aFF\pos(443.949,598.286)}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.03,0:00:15.30,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Shocker is coming,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.73,0:00:18.82,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,with its armies\Nstraight from hell
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.36,0:00:22.92,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Their black shadows\Nthreaten us all
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.92,0:00:26.63,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,but I'll fight to maintain\Nthe peace of our world!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.63,0:00:30.36,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Go! Go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.36,0:00:33.34,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,With my shining machine...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.89,0:00:36.60,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.49,0:00:40.15,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.09,0:00:44.74,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.74,0:00:48.36,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.36,0:00:50.85,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.89,0:00:54.53,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.46,0:00:59.12,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.12,0:01:02.60,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.38,0:01:10.85,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Hongo Takeshi is the Kamen\NRider, a cyborg.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.85,0:01:12.94,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He was modified by the evil\NShocker, a secret
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.94,0:01:14.76,Narrator,,0,0,0,,organization plotting\Nworld domination.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.76,0:01:18.47,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider has pledged to\Nfight Shocker and free humanity!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.01,0:01:25.00,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs165\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(407.167,150.389)}Tsuchigumo Man
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.01,0:01:25.00,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs185\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(577.167,690.389)}Dokumond
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.79,0:01:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What an eerie night...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.86,0:01:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,A liquid explosive that will\Nmelt and burn all metal?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.74,0:01:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,But Sawada...\Ncompleting this will lead to disaster!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.88,0:01:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I think it'll be useful\Nfor industrial purposes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.88,0:02:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Just wait and see.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.87,0:02:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that you, Minoru?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.85,0:02:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Big Brother's\Nstaying out late again.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.40,0:02:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,That stinks.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.09,0:02:14.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted you to help\Nme with my homework.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.91,0:02:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,But if it's for your\Nresearch, I guess you gotta...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.82,0:02:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Good night, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.33,0:02:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't push yourself too hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.73,0:02:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.62,0:02:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Once this invention is complete,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.11,0:02:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take him to the\Nmountains or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.67,0:02:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm off for the night.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.05,0:03:03.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just not working...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.72,0:03:19.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It worked!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.25,0:03:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I've done it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.45,0:03:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's there?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.49,0:04:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.54,0:04:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You saw me, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.58,0:04:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Help me! Someone help!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.67,0:04:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I was sure I saw that\Nspider monster...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.32,0:04:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.98,0:04:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.79,0:04:30.99,Narrator,,0,0,0,,This terrifying monster is\NShocker's Tsuchigumo Man, Dokumond.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.14,0:04:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,His invention is complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.51,0:04:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we should go.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.39,0:04:41.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.68,0:04:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,He's writing down his\Nresearch data now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.25,0:04:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll take that in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.96,0:04:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.61,0:04:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I've sorted out all the data\Nabout the liquid explosive.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.19,0:05:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Morning already?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.05,0:05:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me that bag!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.42,0:05:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.36,0:05:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,After him!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.26,0:05:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't let him escape! Get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.01,0:05:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn! You won't catch me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.32,0:05:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Catch him! Catch him, quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.17,0:06:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,After him! Go after him!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.93,0:06:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.33,0:06:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo Takeshi...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.58,0:06:47.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Be on your guard!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.83,0:06:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Shocker!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.39,0:06:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What have you done?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.78,0:06:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.14,0:07:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Die, Hongo!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.81,0:07:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.04,0:07:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Transformation!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.27,0:07:43.81,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\an7\c&HECCDB5&\3c&H716550&}Municipal Hospital
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.21,0:07:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be all right, Minoru.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.10,0:07:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,He'll get better right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.86,0:08:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Director, can he be saved?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.10,0:08:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,He's in very bad shape.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.95,0:08:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,We've done one surgery,\Nbut we need to leave him be overnight,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.29,0:08:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,then do another surgery\Nin the afternoon to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.79,0:08:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.61,0:08:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Cheer up! It'll be okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.30,0:08:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.70,0:08:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,The monster... help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.44,0:08:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Sawada, speak to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.50,0:08:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,- Big Brother!\N- Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.88,0:08:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Bring the instruments.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.84,0:08:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.67,0:08:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It's chasing me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.08,0:08:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll never...\Ngive you my research!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.26,0:08:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Sawada!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.60,0:08:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Go to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.67,0:08:48.57,Italics,,0,0,0,,Damn you, Shocker...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.57,0:08:51.13,Italics,,0,0,0,,So it's Sawada's\Nresearch they were after?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.67,0:08:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.64,0:08:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You've failed completely!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.93,0:09:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Our plan to dissolve everything\Nin Japan made of metal...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.76,0:09:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,everything from\Nships to airplanes...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.63,0:09:09.39,Default,,0,0,0,,has gone up in smoke!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.07,0:09:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You failed to steal the research\Ndata, and by killing Doctor Sawada,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.91,0:09:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,you've ensured there's no one left who\Ncan make more of the liquid explosive!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.10,0:09:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm very sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.41,0:09:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You great fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.33,0:09:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll be put to death at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.54,0:09:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait. Doctor Sawada is still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.52,0:09:33.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You must follow up\Non your plan at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.05,0:09:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,He's alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.68,0:09:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Does that mean Hongo saved him?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.00,0:09:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I have the perfect plan in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.62,0:09:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll extract his brain before he\Ndies and turn him into a cyborg.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.86,0:09:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Then he'll have to make\Nthe explosive for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.61,0:10:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Dokumond!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.21,0:10:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Abduct him from the\Nhospital at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.19,0:10:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.10,0:10:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,How were things at the hospital?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.34,0:10:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,They won't know until they do\Nthe follow-up surgery tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.52,0:10:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It's awful that Minoru's brother\Nhas to go through this...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.91,0:10:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Could it be Shocker again?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.22,0:10:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.\NThey were after Sawada's data.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.72,0:10:26.93,Default,,0,0,0,,But the data burned\Nup in the car!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.74,0:10:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,But Shocker won't give up that\Neasily, I'll bet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.26,0:10:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.06,0:10:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Only Sawada knows the\Nsecrets of his research.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.10,0:10:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Shocker will surely\Ncome after him again.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.62,0:10:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,But Mr. Sawada is in a coma\Nin the hospital, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.39,0:10:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Poor guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.05,0:10:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Knowing them,\Nthey'll still try it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.43,0:10:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway...\Nwill you look after Minoru?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.90,0:10:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't want him abducted.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.96,0:10:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Just leave it to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.54,0:10:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.11,0:11:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Cheer up, Minoru.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.98,0:11:01.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.71,0:11:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Just you watch me...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.26,0:11:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,They tricked us!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.01,0:12:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been waiting, Shocker.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.72,0:12:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew I'd find you behind this!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.96,0:12:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You wretch, Hongo Takeshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.97,0:12:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Behold the skills of the Tsuchigumo\NMan, Dokumond!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.77,0:12:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.93,0:12:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Transformation!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.11,0:12:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Shocker!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.41,0:13:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I need a plan...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.03,0:13:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't over!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.83,0:13:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki, you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.78,0:13:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.29,0:13:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,They're awfully\Npersistent, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.03,0:13:17.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Shocker never gives up easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.36,0:13:26.24,Bumper Episode 53-69,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fs90\pos(280,94)\c&H05008E&}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.57,0:13:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What are they up to?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.73,0:13:41.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.73,0:13:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.45,0:13:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you people want?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.01,0:13:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Get out of there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.00,0:13:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.03,0:13:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.16,0:14:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't escape now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.98,0:14:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.88,0:14:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,- Excuse me, nurse.\N- Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.30,0:14:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Prepare the patient Sawada\Nfor surgery at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.82,0:14:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Wasn't that scheduled\Nfor this afternoon?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.39,0:14:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Just do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.06,0:14:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.83,0:14:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,The director is acting strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.98,0:14:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Not at all like\Nhis usual self...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.00,0:14:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey. Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.14,0:14:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Sawada's getting surgery.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.46,0:14:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Wasn't it going to\Nbe this afternoon?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.64,0:14:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Has he regained consciousness?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.83,0:14:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,No, not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.12,0:14:59.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's check it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.67,0:15:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.47,0:15:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,There's been a change of plans.\NI'm doing the surgery now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.51,0:15:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be the witness, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.16,0:15:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,No, we don't need a witness.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.95,0:15:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,But the regulations...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.78,0:15:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll call you in later, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.93,0:15:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do the checkup\Nand anesthetic first.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.26,0:15:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Now,\Nget him to the operating room.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.86,0:15:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.53,0:15:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't like that director guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.44,0:15:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes... but he wasn't\Nacting like that yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.17,0:15:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe that's just how\Ngreat doctors are.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.59,0:16:04.31,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fs60\c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&}2nd Operating Room
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.73,0:16:04.31,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\an3\3c&HFFFFFF&\c&H3B3CFF&}Surgery in Progress
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.65,0:16:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Take the man at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.18,0:16:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,That checkup is taking a long\Ntime, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.87,0:16:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, maybe that's just\Nhow these things are.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.02,0:16:46.14,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\an8\3c&HFFFFFF&\c&H3B3CFF&}Surgery in Progress
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.15,0:16:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn... it's started already.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.74,0:16:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.71,0:16:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Something's off about all this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.74,0:16:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey. Are you sure about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.54,0:16:58.65,Default,,0,0,0,,We just have to try it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.88,0:17:03.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Nurse! Nurse!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.73,0:17:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Speak to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.00,0:17:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn, they were disguised\Nas the director!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.03,0:17:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you, Shocker!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.18,0:17:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did they take Mr. Sawada?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.53,0:17:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen to me.\NDiscard all other parts of his body.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.79,0:17:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Remove only the\Nbrain for transfer.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.09,0:17:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.95,0:17:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is the prisoner\Nset to receive it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.72,0:17:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.47,0:17:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Here he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.94,0:17:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Very good.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.85,0:17:43.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Prepare them for\Nsurgery at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.64,0:17:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the Sawada household.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.70,0:17:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.54,0:17:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the director's house.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.30,0:17:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What do the three\Nhave in common?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.25,0:18:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no use.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.52,0:18:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I'm barking\Nup the wrong tree...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.95,0:18:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It's already 11 o'clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.51,0:18:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to get him back\Nby noon for surgery,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.57,0:18:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,or it'll be too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.69,0:18:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Brother... don't die!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.13,0:18:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, don't think like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.78,0:18:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm back!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.97,0:18:17.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Shouldn't you be\Nat the hospital?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.97,0:18:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Goro!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.08,0:18:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with you?\NShow a little respect!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.35,0:18:24.31,Default,,0,0,0,,At least for Minoru's sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.31,0:18:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you guys so mad about?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.90,0:18:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I went out to catch\Nspiders outside
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.37,0:18:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,to do research on that\NTsuchigumo spider monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.25,0:18:34.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You could at least\Nshow some appreciation.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.65,0:18:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.24,0:18:40.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course,\Nthis isn't a Tsuchigumo spider, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.95,0:18:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.24,0:18:44.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Goro, you did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.86,0:18:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,How can spiders walk around on their\Nown webs without getting trapped?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.65,0:18:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because their feet\Ngenerate a special oil.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.13,0:18:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, if I track\NDokumond's footsteps from the window,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.00,0:19:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I can find their base.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.74,0:19:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you really track\Na spider's footsteps?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.46,0:19:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Transformation!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.33,0:19:40.76,Narrator,,0,0,0,,As a cyborg, Hongo Takeshi possesses\Neyes twenty times sharper than a human's.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.32,0:19:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.22,0:19:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Begin the surgery.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.89,0:20:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this the place?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.56,0:20:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,There you are, Shocker!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.95,0:20:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Fight me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.09,0:20:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki, you handle things here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.03,0:21:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.91,0:21:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,The Kamen Rider is here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.85,0:21:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Get rid of him!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.18,0:21:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Dokumond,\Nthis is all on your head!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.59,0:21:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.59,0:21:31.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, step outside!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.94,0:20:25.46,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Shocker is coming,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.46,0:20:28.52,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,with its armies\Nstraight from hell
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.05,0:20:32.55,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Their black shadows\Nthreaten us all
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.55,0:20:36.07,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,but I'll fight to maintain\Nthe peace of our world!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.07,0:20:39.78,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Go! Go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.78,0:20:43.31,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,With my shining machine...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.31,0:20:46.00,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.89,0:20:49.60,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.39,0:20:54.03,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.03,0:20:57.66,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.65,0:21:08.31,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Shocker is coming,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.31,0:21:11.58,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,with its armies made of demons
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.59,0:21:15.41,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Their black shadows\Nthreaten our friends,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.41,0:21:18.99,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,but I'll fight to maintain\Nthe peace of our world!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.99,0:21:22.56,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Go! Go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.56,0:21:26.26,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,With my scarf of red...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.26,0:21:28.72,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.59,0:21:32.55,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.42,0:21:36.95,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.95,0:21:40.76,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.79,0:21:51.39,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Shocker is coming
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.39,0:21:54.41,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,with its armies spreading fear
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.02,0:21:58.55,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Their black shadows\Nthreaten our towns,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.55,0:22:02.14,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,but I'll fight to maintain\Nthe peace of our world!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.14,0:22:05.81,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Go! Go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.81,0:22:09.26,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,With my mask of green...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.26,0:22:12.01,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.99,0:22:15.78,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.57,0:22:20.15,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.15,0:22:24.02,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.12,0:22:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.94,0:22:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You all right, Rider?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.25,0:22:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Look! Dokumond is finished!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.48,0:23:01.22,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The surgery saved\NDoctor Sawada's life,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.22,0:23:03.65,Narrator,,0,0,0,,and his research on the liquid\Nexplosive was protected.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.65,0:23:06.72,Narrator,,0,0,0,,But there was no telling how\Nlong Shocker would continue
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.72,0:23:09.38,Narrator,,0,0,0,,to challenge Hongo\NTakeshi, the Kamen Rider.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.38,0:23:10.93,Cont,,0,50,150,,{\blur.8\fad(0,400)}To be continued
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.16,0:23:12.85,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\4aFF\bord0\b1\fs67.5\fnCalibri\pos(499.031,496.481)}Next Episode Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.12,0:23:15.15,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The next assassin sent by Shocker\NHQ to kill our Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.15,0:23:16.85,Narrator,,0,0,0,,is the monstrous Beaded Lizard Man.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.85,0:23:18.79,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Beaded Lizard Man spits a red venom
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.79,0:23:22.85,Narrator,,0,0,0,,and our Kamen Rider uses his new\Ntechnique, the Head Crusher, to fight him.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.85,0:23:25.24,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Join us next week for\N"The Monstrous Beaded Lizard Man.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.24,0:23:28.09,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Deathmatch in Fear Valley!!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.24,0:23:31.07,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx90\fs135\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(483.167,140.389)}The Monstrous Beaded Lizard Man
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.24,0:23:31.07,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs135\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(477.167,690.389)}Deathmatch in Fear Valley!!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.89,0:23:40.73,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,He came here on a storm...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.31,0:23:43.31,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Who is he? Who is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.31,0:23:45.27,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Who is this man of storms,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.27,0:23:48.32,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,who sends the\Nvillains scattering?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.82,0:23:50.69,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.69,0:23:52.57,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,His mask stands for justice!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.57,0:23:54.36,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Start it up! Rev it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.36,0:23:55.81,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Get that engine running!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.20,0:23:58.20,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Give me top speed, Cyclone!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.25,0:24:03.97,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Hit them with\Nall of your anger!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.97,0:24:07.50,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Put an end to Shocker's evil!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.50,0:24:11.10,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider! Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.59,0:24:15.52,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Comment: 0,0:01:20.01,0:01:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsuchigumo Man Dokumond
Comment: 0,0:23:28.24,0:23:31.04,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The Monstrous Beaded Lizard Man\NDeathmatch in Fear Valley!!